{{see|Wink}}

==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪŋk|-ɪŋk]]

===Verb===
'''to wink''' [[intransitive]]
#To [[blink]] with only one [[eye]] as a [[message]], [[signal]], or [[suggestion]]
#To [[twinkle]]
'''to wink''' [[transitive]]
#To send a message by winking

===Noun===
'''wink'''
#An act of winking (a blink), or a message sent by winking
#A [[brief]] [[time]]; an [[instant]]
#A twinkle
#A brief [[period]] of [[sleep]]; especially [[forty winks]]
#A disc used in the game of [[tiddlywinks]]

